  "entrance_narration": [
    "[color=#6cb4c4][b]The Welcome Wench[/b][/color]\nThe heavy oak door swings open and warmth floods over you. A long bar counter dominates the center of the room, candlelight dancing across polished wood. The smell of roasting meat and spilled ale fills the air.",
    "[color=#d9d566]Barkeep Marta[/color] looks up from behind the bar, sizing you up with practiced eyes. To the left, [color=#d9d566]Old Tom[/color] hunches over his ale at a dining table. Near the stairs, a [color=#d9d566]hooded figure[/color] watches from the shadows. A [color=#d9d566]quest board[/color] near the bar bristles with notices."
  ]
